    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月ストがBIG4になってしばらく経った頃",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、{user}さん\n今日の収録は長丁場でしたね",
      "startTime": 5.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。しかし三本録りの予定が\n急遽一本増えるとは思わなかったよ",
      "startTime": 12.1999993007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "疲れているところ悪いんだが、帰る前に\n明日の予定をもう一度確認しておこうか",
      "startTime": 18.033332634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "午前中にライブの打ち合わせ、午後にラジオ収録と\nインタビュー、それから特番のゲスト出演ですよね",
      "startTime": 25.6666659673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "今までもそれなりに忙しくさせてもらってると思って\nましたけど……BIG4になった影響は大きいですね",
      "startTime": 34.233332634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "朝から分刻みのスケジュールだけど、大丈夫か？\nさすがに休む時間が少な過ぎるよな",
      "startTime": 43.2666659673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です。仕事を受けるかどうかは毎回確認を\nとってくれてるじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 50.6199106369,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "それに、サニピがBIG4になった時の目の回るような\n忙しさを目の前で見てましたから。想定内です",
      "startTime": 57.3666659673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "頼もしいな。確かにあの時期のサニピは\n忙しさに慣れてないこともあって大変だったからな",
      "startTime": 66.0999993007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "五人とも毎朝バタバタ準備をしてましたよ\nいつの間にかみんな慣れてましたけど",
      "startTime": 74.1666659673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "あの頃は「さくら達はこんなに沢山の人に\n必要とされてるんだな」って羨ましく思ってました",
      "startTime": 81.0999993007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今は私達も……これまで以上に\n必要としてもらえている。それが嬉しくて",
      "startTime": 90.233332634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "それに以前から応援してくれているファンのみなさんは\n月ストのBIG4入りを心から喜んでくれてるんです",
      "startTime": 98.940378213,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "これまでの道のりを考えると\n辛い思いをさせてしまった瞬間もあったと思います",
      "startTime": 105.6666705449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "それでも変わらず私達を応援して、心から\n喜んでくれている。そんな人達の想いに応えたいんです",
      "startTime": 113.3666705449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "だから、これからもどんどん\nお仕事を受けさせて下さい",
      "startTime": 120.7160140052,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5917.3232063999985,
          "startTime": 126.6333372116
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。だけど、無理はしないようにな？\n……ん？　電話だ、ちょっとすまない",
      "startTime": 127.2666705449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "はい、はい、なるほど……了解しました\n一度検討いたしますね。はい、それでは失礼します",
      "startTime": 136.0000089645,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "新しいお仕事の話ですか？",
      "startTime": 141.100008869,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。月ストへの依頼だったんだが……\n今日は時間も時間だし、明日にするか",
      "startTime": 147.3000038783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "お仕事をどんどん受けさせて下さい……って\nさっき言いましたよね。話だけでも聞かせて下さい",
      "startTime": 153.9000038783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "やる気満々だな。分かった。そろそろ撤収しないと\nいけないから、事務所で話そうか",
      "startTime": 163.3666705449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "今度、地方で開かれる音楽フェスがあるんだが\n月ストに出演依頼がきてるんだ。資料を見てくれるか",
      "startTime": 171.9247798696,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4641.890675300005,
          "startTime": 176.5666705449
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "音楽フェスですか。今回が第一回なんですね",
      "startTime": 176.3333422023,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7389.995009300009,
          "startTime": 183.7233372116
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "現時点での出演者一覧を見ると分かると思うけど\nかなり気合いが入ったイベントになりそうなんだ",
      "startTime": 185.9000038783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "有名な歌手やアイドルが沢山……\n確かに凄いです",
      "startTime": 192.3784691486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "主催者の方は「ぜひ月ストにヘッドライナーを」と\nおっしゃってるんだが……スケジュールがネックでな",
      "startTime": 198.0333372116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "あ……なるほど。確かこのフェスの次の日は\n新曲のMV撮影がありましたよね？",
      "startTime": 207.8333372116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだ。イベントに出演するとなると\n移動時間も相まって負荷が高い。どうする？",
      "startTime": 214.2666705449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "ぜひ出演させて下さい\n今は少しでも沢山の人の前で歌いたいんです",
      "startTime": 220.9666705449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。渚達にも聞いてみるよ。それにしても……\n最近の琴乃は本当に元気一杯だな",
      "startTime": 230.3666705449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
